@@TJvCustomNavigationPane.NavPanelFont
Summary
  Specifies the font used on the buttons.
Description
  Use NavPanelFont to set the font used on the buttons in the control. The button font is separate from the
  normal font. The normal font is used to specify the font settings for the page itself.
See Also
